oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This work focuses on the structural elements of a vehicle, AHSS materials used to make them and suitable welding methods. There are also a couple of examples to compare which method is most appropriate in two different cases of two pieces that have been selected.

oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Material and technological analysis of car bodywork elements
